  <afflictiondescription.ba_smoke_inhalation>双眼通红、不断流泪，胸腔深处发出刺耳的咳嗽。</afflictiondescription.ba_smoke_inhalation>
  <afflictioncauseofdeath.ba_smoke_inhalation>因吸入烟雾而窒息。</afflictioncauseofdeath.ba_smoke_inhalation>
